<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy" %>

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-6 w-full max-w-2xl max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <button onclick="toggleModal()" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-red-500 text-2xl font-bold">&times;</button>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> May 7, 2025</p>
      
      <p><strong>1. Information We Collect:</strong> 
          We gather various types of personal information, including but not limited to your name, email address, property preferences, geographic location, and any data you share during your interactions with our AI assistant. Additionally, we may collect metadata such as device information, browser type, IP address, and usage patterns to better understand how you engage with our platform.
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>2. Use of Data:</strong> 
          Your data is primarily used to enhance your experience on our platform. This includes matching you with the most suitable real estate listings, generating intelligent AI responses, saving your favorite properties, and providing personalized recommendations. We also use your data to improve our algorithms, conduct analytics, and troubleshoot issues.
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>3. Sharing:</strong> 
          We do not sell your personal data to third parties. We only share information with trusted third-party service providers who help us operate our platform (such as cloud hosting, analytics, and customer support services), and only to the extent necessary for them to perform their functions. All third parties are contractually obligated to protect your data and comply with relevant privacy laws.
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>4. Security:</strong> 
          We implement industry-standard measures to safeguard your data, including SSL encryption, secure data storage, periodic security audits, and strict access controls. Our security practices are designed to prevent unauthorized access, data breaches, and loss of information.
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>5. Your Rights:</strong> 
          You have the right to access, update, correct, or delete your personal information stored on our platform. You may also withdraw consent or restrict certain types of data processing. To exercise these rights, simply contact our support team or access the privacy settings in your account dashboard.
      </p>
      
      <p><strong>6. Changes:</strong> 
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in legal requirements, technology, or our business practices. If any significant changes are made, we will notify you via email or through prominent in-app alerts. Continued use of the platform constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>